OpenSync Framework
==================

OpenSync is a plugin-based application that basically provides a framework
for syncing groups which can have two or more members. 

This is the Akonadi (KDE 4.x) PIM synchronisation framework

Requirements
============
- libopensync1 (v.0.40)


Installation
============
export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=/opt/custom/opensync/lib/pkgconfig

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$prefix /path/to/opensync/source/
make
make install

Links
=====

